    • isDetachedGraph

      public boolean isDetachedGraph()
      Check if the object is in a detached graph It is in a detached graph if the parent is a node but sceneGraphObject parent is null It is the case for node added to clip, shape, ...
      Returns:
      true if in detached graph/ false if is in the main graph

    • isViewable

      public boolean isViewable()
      Check if the object is viewable. A node is viewable if all the parents are instance of node
      Returns:
      true if viewable
